vlan 50
name PRINCIPAL

vlan 60
name GUIDANCE

vlan 70
name SERVER

vlan 200
name VOICE

Gawin ito sa lahat ng Access Switch.

STEP 2
Assign Data VLAN

Example

interface range fa0/1-5
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10

Admin

interface range fa0/7-9
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 20

Faculty

interface range fa0/11-18
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 30

Pareho lang sa ibang VLAN.

STEP 3
Assign Voice VLAN

Ito ang bagong command.

IT Department

interface range fa0/1-5
switchport voice vlan 200

Admin

interface range fa0/7-9
switchport voice vlan 200

Faculty

interface range fa0/11-18
switchport voice vlan 200

Mapapansin mo hindi mo inalis ang Data VLAN.

Example

switchport access vlan 10
switchport voice vlan 200

Magkasama sila.

STEP 4
Configure Trunk Links

Sa lahat ng uplinks

interface g0/1
switchport mode trunk

Kung lumabas ang error

Command rejected:
An interface whose trunk encapsulation is "Auto"
cannot be configured to "trunk" mode

Gamitin muna

switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
switchport mode trunk

Verify

show cdp neighbors
show interfaces trunk
